precis:
Order (a) authorizing Canadians to accept and wear the UNITED NATIONS
HEADQUARTERS MEDAL in recognition of honourable service at UN Headquarters
in New York City for a period of at least 90 days, and (b) establishing its
order of precedence in the Canadian Honours System.
